        </mml:math>
      </disp-formula>
      <p>To reduce the inflation effects of redundant concepts on the uniConSig scores, we penalized the scores based on the similarity matrix of molecular concepts associated with each Gene<sub><italic toggle="yes">x</italic></sub> in the genome (<xref rid="btad325-F1" ref-type="fig">Fig. 1C</xref>). We generated the similarity matrix by computing the Ochiai index between molecular concepts.
</p>
